### 1. Health Check
# Expected: 200 OK
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### 2. About
# Expected: 200 OK
GET http://localhost:8080/api/about

### 3. Get all tickets
# Expected: 200 OK
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets

### 4. Get one existing ticket
# Expected: 200 OK
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/T001

### 5. Get one missing ticket
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/T999

### 6. Create a valid ticket
# Expected: 201 Created
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "VPN connection not working",
  "description": "User cannot connect to company VPN from home.",
  "category": "Network",
  "priority": "MEDIUM",
  "createdBy": "siti@example.com"
}

### 7. Create an invalid ticket (missing/blank required fields)
# Expected: 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "",
  "category": "",
  "priority": "",
  "createdBy": ""
}
